name: Urban Boomtown
title: Fastest Urban Population Growth
description: In 2023, Oman experienced a remarkable urban population growth rate of 7.27%, the highest globally. This rapid urbanization reflects the country's dynamic development and modernization efforts.

name: Industrial Powerhouse
title: High Employment in Industry
description: As of 2023, 40.16% of Oman's workforce is employed in the industrial sector, showcasing the country's strong industrial base and economic diversification.

name: Population Surge
title: Rapid Population Growth
description: Oman's population grew by 6.53% in 2023, one of the highest rates worldwide, indicating a vibrant and expanding society.

name: Arab Trade Hub
title: Major Importer from Arab World
description: In 2023, 53.13% of Oman's merchandise imports came from Arab countries, highlighting its strong trade ties within the region.

name: Safe Haven for Women
title: Lowest Female Suicide Rate
description: Oman recorded a female suicide mortality rate of just 0.21 per 100,000 in 2021, the lowest globally, reflecting a supportive environment for women's mental health.
